retive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span> [\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] ọ proco (n) s (uli) c (larissimo) · v (iro) \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span> [\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">..\u003C/span> ị optimo \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"author":3,"date":4,"citedRange":852,"ptr":853,"ref":854,"title":2,"citation":5},"20 no.10 fig.3",{"target":227},{"_":229,"target":229}],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
